data.description: BEAUTIFUL 4 bedroom 2 and a half bath home in highly sought after Villages of Woodland Springs and Keller ISD! Home features BRAND NEW carpet, FRESH Paint, NEW sod, NEW roof and decorative fireplace, granite countertops and gas cooktop. This home is MOVE IN READY! Neighborhood offers 6 community pools, walking trails, catch and release ponds, playgrounds, and more! Great location! Close to shopping, entertainment, and dining. Easy access to major roads and highways. Come see today before it’s too late!
